msContents.summary: Originally folded, archival copies of documents, comprising a report to the governor of Milan after a year spent at the court of the Holy Roman Empire at the time of the Imperial Diet in Ratisbon until the 1664 treaty with the Turks. Describes Emperor Leopold I, his court, administrative and military functions, personalities, etc.
